## Attribution Notice

This project was developed for the AWS Breaking Barriers Virtual Challenge 2025. The goal is to demonstrate how AWS generative AI services can be combined with edge computing to create meaningful accessibility solutions.

SignToMe aims to break communication barriers for the deaf and hard-of-hearing community through real-time sign language interpretation technology.